quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  39,1,"Jippagol deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, poolu…óo, √Īee√Īo oon."
  39,2,"Min njippiniirii deftere nden e maa…óa, e hoore goonga. rewu allah, la…ď…ďinanaa mo diina ka."
  39,3,"Ngaanndee, ko Allah woodani diina laa…ďuka kan. ∆Āeen non …ďe …ďeya nogitori yi…ó…ďe ga makko (hara hi…ďe wi'a): ""Min ngaalaa rewirde …ói, si wonaa tun no …ói …ďannira min ka Allah, …ďadal"". Pellet, Allah √Ďaawoyat hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, e kon ko …ďe woni lurrude e mun. Pellet, Allah feewnata on gon…óo fewnoowo, …óuu…óu…óo jeddugol."
  39,4,"Sinno Allah yi…óno, nde o siforta …ďi…ó…óo, O su…ďayno ko o yi…ói woo, e ko o tagi kon. Senaare woodanii mo ! Ko KaŇčko woni Allah, Bajjo, poolu…óo on."
  39,5,"O tagirii kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin, goonga.Homo suddira jemma on √Īalaema oon, O suddira √Īalawma on jemma on. O eelti na'ange ngen e lewru ndun, kala majji no doga haa e lajal ta∆īaangal. Nganndee, ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo, kaforoowo On."
  39,6,"O tagii on e fittaandu wooturu, refi Owa…ói e ndun, genndo mayru. O jippinani on e neemoraa…ói …óin, nooneeji jeetati. Homo taga on ka teege yumma mon en, tagu …ďaawo tagu, e ndeer ni…ďe tati. Ko On moo…óon Allah, woni Joomi mon ! Ko KaŇčko laamu woodani. Dewetee…óo alaa, si wonaa Allah. Ko honno perlitora…óon [e dewugol Mo]?"
  39,7,"Si on njeddii, anndon Allah, ko jondinii…óo e mon. O ja…ďantaa jiyaa…ďe makko …ďeen, ke'eferaaku. Si on njettii Mo noon, O weltanoo on …óuum.Hay gooto roondantaako go…ó…óo woo donngal mum. Refti ko ka Joomi mon, woni ruttorde mon; O yeetitoo on, fii kon ko gollatno…óon. Pellet, ko O ganndu…óo, ko woni e …ďer…óe."
  39,8,"Si loraa memii ne…ó…óo on, o noddira Joomi makko, ruttagol e makko. Refti si O okkii mo mo∆ī∆īere, immorde ka makko, o yejjita ko o noddatno kon ado …óuum, o wa…óana Allah kafidii…ói, fii no o majjinira (yim…ďe …ďeen) e laawol makko ngol. MaAku: ""Dakmitor keeferaaku maa ngun, see…óa. Pellet, ko a jiyaa…óo e yim…ďe Yiite …ďeen""."
  39,9,"Kaa ko on yankinotoo…óo tummbo jemma, ko o cujjoowo, darotoo…óo (naafe), hara homo La'akara, homo joortii yurmeende Joomi makko nden... Maaku: ""Hara anndu…ďe …ďen fotay e …ďe nganndaa …ďen?"" Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraa…ďe haqqille …ďeen."
  39,10,"Maaku: ""eey mon yo jiyaa…ďe Am gooŇč…óin…ďe, kulee Joomi mon"". Hino woodani mo∆ī∆īim…ďe (golle) …ďen e oo aduna, mbarjaari. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi. Nganndee mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďeen timminirante njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin, ko aldaa e limoore."
  39,11,"Maaku: ""Miin mi yamiraama dewugol Allah, la…ď…ďinana mo diina kan,"
  39,12,"Mi yamiraa kadi, gongol arano e jebbilii…ďe …ďeen""."
  39,13,"Maaku : ""Miin mi…óo huli, si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte √Ďalaande Mawnde""."
  39,14,"Maaku: ""Ko Allah mi rewata, mi la…ď…ďinan mo diina am."
  39,15,"ndewee ko nji…óu…óon onon, hara wonaa KaŇčko. Maaku: ""Ko woni hayru…ďe …ďen, ko …ďeen …ďe tawata √Ďande Darngal, …ďe hayrinii ko'e ma…ď…ďe, e …ďeynguureeji ma…ď…ďe"". Nganndee ko nden woni hayrere …ďanngunde ndeen."
  39,16,"Hino woodirani …ďe seŇčgo dow ma…ď…ďe, kippoodi Yiite, e kippoodi senngo ley ma…ď…ďe. Ko …óum woni ko Allah hul…ďinirta jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Ko onon yo jiyaa…ďe Am, kori kulee Kam!"
  39,17,"∆Āeen wo…ó…óitor…ďe rewugol bewnooji …ói, …ďe nduttii e Allah, welo-welo no woodani …ďe. Wewlinir jiyaa…ďe am …ďeen,"
  39,18,"nanoo…ďe Konngol …ďeen, …ďe njokka ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e maggol. Ko …ďeen woni …ďe Allah feewni …ďen, ko …ďen ngoni joomiraa…ďe haqqille …ďeen."
  39,19,"E ko on mo konngol lepte jojji e mum... E ko aan da…óndata gon…óo ka Yiite?"
  39,20,"Si ko …ďen hul…ďe Joomi mun, hino woodani …ďe ku…ďeeje [ka Aljanna] e ku…ďeeje mahaa…óe dow majje, hara can…ói no ila ley majje. Ko fodoore Allah ! Allah non firtataa fodoore."
  39,21,"E a yiaani, won'de Allah saa∆īinirii ndiyam ka kammu, o naadi …óam e ndeer …ďulli ka leydi; refti o yaltinira …óam remuru seedundu noone, refti ndu …óay…óa, yi'aa hindu soy…ói; refti O wa…óa …óum ko muncaa. Pellet, wonii e …óuum, waaju, wonan'de joomiraa…ďe haqqille …ďeen."
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah ya√Ī√Īani …ďendre mum nden, fii lislaamu, hara homo e ndaygu immorde ka Joomi makko... Bone woodanii …ďen yooru…ďe …ďer…óe mum, e jantagol Allah. ∆Āeen ngonii e majjere …ďanngunde."
  39,23,"Allah jippinii ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e yeewtere, deftere nanndunde [√Īaawooje], …óimmitunde. Nde guri …ďen huloo…ďe Joomi muyn ri…ďirta (nanugol nde), refti guri e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe dee∆īira jaŇčtoore Allah nden. Ko …óuum woni peewal Allah ngal O feewnira on mo muuyani. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray peewnoowo mo alaa."
  39,24,"E ko on reentarii…óo yeeso mun ngon, e lepte bon…óe …óen √Ďande Darngal... Too√Īu…ďe …ďen mbi'anee on tuma: ""Mee…óee kon ko ngonno…óon faggitanaade""."
  39,25,"Adinoo…ďe …ďen njeddiino, lepte …óeen ardirani …ďe, ka …ďe tinaani."
  39,26,"Allah mee…óiniri …ďe koyeera, ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet non, ko lepte La'akara …óen noon, …ďuri mawnude, si tawno he…ďe nganndunoo!"
  39,27,"Goo…óii Min piyanii yim…ďe …ďeen, e ndee Alqur'aanaare, kala misal, mbelejo'o, …ďe mbaajitora."
  39,28,"Alqur'aanaare (janngeteende) e haala aarabi, nde aldaa e oo√Īaare, fii no …ďe ngooŇč…óira."
  39,29,"Allah wa…óii yeru, gorko mo lurru…ďe hawti …óum, he…ďe poo…óondira mo, e gorko laa…ďan…óo gorko [goo]: Hara …ďen …ói…óo fotay e misal? Yettoore woodanii Allah! Kono …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe nganndaa."
  39,30,"Pellet, aan ko a maayoowo, kam…ďe kadi ko …ďe maayoo…ďe;"
  39,31,"refti onon, √Ďande Darngal, ko to Joomi mon, njeddondiroyton."
  39,32,"E ko hommbo …ďuri too√Īde wa on jeddu…óo …óo e hoore Allah, maa o yeddi goonga kan nde ko arunoo e makko? E wonaa Jahannama woni jaa∆īorde yeddu…ďe …ďeen?"
  39,33,"Oon noon gardu…óo e goonga, o goongini …óuum, ko …ďen ngoni gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen."
  39,34,"Hino woodani kala ko …ďe paaletee, ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe; ko …óuum njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  39,35,"fii no Allah yaawtirana …ďe, ko …ďuri bon'de e ko …ďe golli kon, O yo…ďitira …ďe njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndiin, ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e ko …ďe ngollaynoo kon."
  39,36,"Allah siforaali yonugol jiyaa…óo makko on? He…ďe kul…ďinire …óin …ói wonaa mo. Kala mo Allah majjini, haray Feewnoowo alanaa mo."
  39,37,"Kala non mo Allah feewni, majjinoowo mo alaa. Allah siforaali won'de poolu…óo, Jom lepte?"
  39,38,"Pellet, si a la…ďndike …ďe: ""Ko hommbo tagi kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin?"", ma …ďe mbi'u: ""Ko Allah"". Maaku: ""Yeewtee kam fii …óin …ói ndewoton ga Allah, si Allah faandanike lam lorra, hara …ói huncanay kam lorra makko kan? Maa si o faandanike lam yurmeende, taw si …ói ha…óay kam yurmeende makko nden? Maaku: ""Allah yonii kam, ko e makko hoolnotoo…ďe …ďen tuuginotoo""."
  39,39,"Maaku: ""eey mon yim…ďe am, ngollee e laawol mon, min ko e [laawol am] mi ngollirta. Aray ka nganndon."
  39,40,"ko hommbo lepte koynay…óe ngaroyat e muu…óum, lepte duumii…óe njippoo e makko."
  39,41,"Min njippinirii deftere nden e maa…óa, fii yim…ďe …ďeen, e hoore goonga. Kala peewu…óo, ko hoore makko [o feewani]; kala kadi majju…óo, ko hoore makko o majjani. A wonaani wakiil e dow ma…ď…ďe."
  39,42,"Allah homo ∆īettita pittaali …óin, saanga maayde majji, e …óin …ói maayaani, ka …óoyngol majji. O jogitoo …óiin …ói √Īaawani maayde, O accita …óiya, haa e lajal ta∆īaangal. Pellet, Ma'andeeji ngoni e …óuum, wona nde yim…ďe miijitotoo…ďe."
  39,43,"Kaa …ďe njogiti tefooji, ga Allah? Maaku: ""Hay si tawii …ói jiyaa hu'unde, …ói haqqiltaa kadi?"""
  39,44,"Maaku: ""Tefoore nden fow, ko Allah heeranii. Ko KaŇčko woodani laamagol kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin. refti ko ka makko nduttete…óon""."
  39,45,"Si fii Allah tun jaŇčtaama, …ďer…ďe …ďen …ďe ngooŇč…óinaa La'akara …ďen, tamoo. Si fii …óiya, …ói wonaa Mo [KaŇčko Allah] jaŇčtaama, e jaka yoo, he…ďe wewla."
  39,46,"Maaku: ""Yaa Allah, pu…ó…óu…óo kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin, ganndu…óo birnii…ói e pee√Ī…ói, ko Aan √Īaawata hakkunde jiyaa…ďe Maa …ďeen, ko …ďe luutondiraynoo e mum""."
  39,47,"Si tawno no woodanno too√Ī…ďe …ďeen, ko woni kon ka leydi fow, e yeru mum, wond'ude e mum, …ďe sottorayno …óum, bone lepte …óen, √Ďande Darngal; fee√Īirana …ďe ka Allah, kon ko …ďe tijjanooki."
  39,48,"boneeji …ói …ďe paggitinoo …óin pe√Īana …ďe, ko …ďe njalkitaynoo kon huu…ďita …ďe."
  39,49,"Si lorra he…ďii ne…ó…óo on, o nodda Min. Refti si Min ngokkii mo neema, immorde ka amen, o wi'a: ""nganndee ko e ganndal [am] mi okkiira …óum"". ∆äuum ko jarrabuyee kan; kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe anndaa."
  39,50,"GooŇč…óii …ďeen adinoo…ďe …ďe mbi'iino …óum. Kono kon ko …ďe paggitotonoo, nafaani …ďe."
  39,51,"boneeji …ói …ďe paggitotonoo …óiin memi …ďe. Too√Ī…ďe …ďeen e ma…ď…ďe, kon ko …ďe wonnoo e paggitagol, memoyat …ďe, …ďe wonaani laawotoo…ďe."
  39,52,"E …ďe nganndaa won'de Allah no ya√Ī√Īana arsike on mo o muuyani, O …ďillina [mo o muuyani]? Pellet, Ma'andeeji ngonii e …óum, wona nde yim…ďe gooŇč…óinoo…ďe."
  39,53,"Maaku: eey mon yo jiyaa…ďe Am fantim…ďe e hoore mum, wota on ta∆īo yurmeende Allah nden. Pellet, Allah ko kaforoowo junubaajo …óin fof. Ko KaŇčko woni kaforoowo, jurmotoo…óo On""."
  39,54,"Tuubee ndutto…óon ka Joomi mon, jebbilano…óon mo, ado lepte …óen arde e mon, hara on paabetaake."
  39,55,"Njokkee ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e ko jippinaa e mon, immorde ka Joomi, ado lepte …óen ado de on, juhal, hara on so'aa anndude."
  39,56,"fii wota woŇčkii wi'oy: ""Ee nimse am, e ko mi welsindii e fii Allah. Pellet, mi jeyano e …ďeen jalkitoo…ďe""."
  39,57,"maa ki wi'a: ""Si Alah feewnuno kam, mi wonanyno jiyaa…óo e gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen""."
  39,58,"Maa ki wi'a, tuma ki yi'ata lepte …óen: ""Si fehre ruttagol no woodannoo kam, mi jeyee e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  39,59,"""Gasataa ! Tawde aayeeje Am …óen aruno e maa…óa, njeddu…óaa …óe, mawnintini…óaa, laati…óaa jiyaa…óo e yeddu…ďe …ďeen""."
  39,60,"√Ďande Darngal, a yi'oya fennonoo…ďe e hoore Allah …ďen, hino …ďawli je'ece. Wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaa∆īorde mawnintinii…ďe …ďeen?"
  39,61,"Allah na da…óndira gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen, sabu maloore ma…ď…ďe nden. Bone memataa …ďeen, wonaa kam…ďe ngoni sunoytoo…ďe."
  39,62,"Ko Allah woni Tak…óo kala hu'unde, ko KaŇčko kadi woni pawtii…óo kala hu'unde."
  39,63,"Ko KaŇčko sottir…óe kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin woodani. Yeddu…ďe aayeeje Allah …ďeen non, ko …ďen ngoni hayru…ďe(pertu…ďe) …ďen."
  39,64,"Maaku: ""E ko woori Allah, njamirton mi, yo mi rew, onon …ďee majju…ďe?"""
  39,65,"GooŇč…óii wahayinaama e maa…óa, e …ďen adinoo…ďe ma: ""Si a sirkii, pellet, golle maa …óeen bonay njeyi…óaa e hayru…ďe …ďeen."
  39,66,"Alah rew Allah, njeye…óaa e yettoo…ďe (Mo) …ďen."
  39,67,"∆Āe mawniniraani Allah, no O foti maninireede, hara le, leydi ndin fof, ko tamannde makko, √Ďande Darngal, kammuuji …óin kadi taggiree √Īaamo makko. Senayee woodanii Mo ! O toowii e kon ko …ďe cirkanta mo."
  39,68,"Wuttee ka Allaandu, kala ko woni ka kammuuji e ka leydi kon fa…ó…óee, si wonaa …ďen …ďe Allah muuyani [da…óugol]. refti wuttee e mayru …ói…óa…ďol, tawa ko …ďe darii…ďe cabbitii."
  39,69,"Leydi ndin jalbira ndaygo Jeydo ndi On; taalkuru nduun wallinee, Annabaa…ďe e seedee…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addee; goonga √Īaawiree hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, wonaa …ďe too√Īetee…ďe;"
  39,70,"woŇčki kala yo…ďee ko golli kon. Ko KaŇčko [Allah] …ďuri anndude ko …ďe ngollata."
  39,71,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen coggiroyee ka Jahannama dente-dente. Haa si …ďe heewtii nge, dame magge udditee, reenu…ďe nge …ďen mbi'ana …ďe: ""E Nulaa…ďe jiyaa…ďe e mo'on heewtaano on, janngaynoo…ďe aayeeje Joomi mon, e moo…óon, …ďe rentina on hawrugol e ndee √Īalaande mon?"" ∆Āe mbi'a: ""Ko non tigiri, kono Konngol lepte ngol, jojjiino e yeddu…ďe …ďeen""."
  39,72,"[∆Āe] mbi'anee: ""Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen lutton ton. Nge bonii jaa∆īorde mawnintinii…ďe …ďeen !""."
  39,73,"Huloo…ďe Joomi mun …ďen kadi …óowitiree ka Aljanna, dente-dente. Haa si …ďe heewtii mo, dame makko udditee, reenu…ďe mo …ďen mbi'ana …ďe: ""Kisal wonii e mon, on laa…ďii, naatiree mo, duumagol""."
  39,74,"∆Āe mbi'a ontuma: ""Jettooje ngoodanii Allah, laatinan…óo men fodoore Mum, O ronini min leydi [Aljanna] ndin, me…óen weerira e Aljanna on, kala ka min nji…ói"". Mbarjaari gollunoo…ďe mo∆ī∆īere …ďeen mo∆ī∆īii."
  39,75,"Yi'oyaa Malaa'ikaen, he…ďe taarii Arsi kin, he…ďe cubbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Goonga √Īaawiree hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Wi'ee on tuma: ""Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo tagoore""."
